      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's the thing though, the \"people who care\" aren't even here. i'm thousands of miles away from everyone i actually know. i look at the people walking past me in the city and it's like we're on different frequencies. if i just stopped showing up, it wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be a quiet gap where a person used to be. it's almost peaceful to think about how little space i actually take up.",
